  "texts": [
    "During the period between 2015 and 2020, terms such as \"visualization,\" \"functions,\" \"complex functions,\" \"mathematics teaching,\" and \"mathematical reasoning\" began to gain prominence.",
    "The software's interactive nature enables the creation of dynamic worksheets that support the visualization of complex numbers and functions (Navetta, 2016).",
    "GeoGebra's integration of modeling, visualization, and programming features has been highlighted in research (Ziatdinov & Valles, 2022. In the most recent period from 2020 to 2023, advanced terms such as \"modeling,\" \"augmented reality,\" \"3D printing,\" \"project-based learning,\" and \"STEAM\" have become emerging trends.",
    "GeoGebra's application has extended to various fields, including geography and differential equations (Soare & Antohe, 2012; Latifi et al., 2022).",
    "The software promotes active learning, interdisciplinary approaches, and the development of mathematical reasoning skills (Sekulić & Takaci, 2013)."
